```text
rule "Turn on lamp after sunset when motion detected"
when
    Item LivingRoom_MotionSensor changed to ON
then
    if (astro:sun:home:set#event.state == "START") {
        sendCommand(LivingRoom_Lamp, ON)
        createTimer(now.plusMinutes(10), [ | 
            sendCommand(LivingRoom_Lamp, OFF) 
        ])
    }
end
```
